on a beach house.

33:00.187 --> 33:02.022
- It's not just a house, Dad.
- You want me to beg, Dad?

33:02.106 --> 33:03.482
'Cause I will. I will.
I'll do whatever you want...

33:03.565 --> 33:06.276
[Belly] The call came early
in the morning.

33:06.360 --> 33:08.862
[pastor] "There is a time
for everything

33:08.946 --> 33:11.073
