that really can't wait.

33:17.788 --> 33:20.499
[pastor] "...and a time to die.

33:20.582 --> 33:23.001
- [crying]
- A time to plant

33:23.085 --> 33:26.797
and a time to uproot."

33:26.880 --> 33:28.590
