34:34.489 --> 34:36.949
Excuse me.

34:37.034 --> 34:39.203
[inhales deeply]

34:39.286 --> 34:41.288
- [vocalizing]
- [music continues]

35:06.021 --> 35:08.982
[Belly] I made a promise
to myself at that moment.

35:09.066 --> 35:11.610
I would not leave his side
for the rest of the day.

35:11.693 --> 35:13.862
He would need me.

35:13.946 --> 35:15.572
