35:19.326 --> 35:21.370
I wonder how Mr. Fisher's doing.

35:22.704 --> 35:26.083
Did Conrad ride
over here with him?

35:26.166 --> 35:27.918
Uh, I don't know.

35:29.461 --> 35:31.588
Thank you for coming.

35:31.672 --> 35:35.843
