a plate of food to you.

35:48.564 --> 35:50.440
No, it's okay.

35:50.524 --> 35:53.318
No, it's-it's no problem.

35:55.153 --> 35:56.572
Okay.

35:56.655 --> 35:58.365
Thank you.

35:59.992 --> 36:03.453
♪ And did you say
that she loved you? ♪

36:03.537 --> 36:05.497
[quiet chatter]

36:05.581 --> 36:09.751
♪ Baby, I don't wanna know...

36:10.752 --> 36:12.462
