36:12.546 --> 36:14.798
Why didn't you wear the one
I left out on your bed?

36:16.967 --> 36:19.011
Um, this was
Susannah's favorite.

36:19.094 --> 36:20.262
I wore it for her.

36:20.345 --> 36:24.725
♪ So I begin not to love you ♪

36:24.808 --> 36:26.852
♪ Turn around, see me running...

36:26.935 --> 36:29.521
Uh, one of those
is for Jere, right?

36:29.605 --> 36:30.898
Yeah.

36:30.981 --> 36:32.482
I'll-I'll just go up
and take it to him.

36:32.566 --> 36:35.861
Okay. Yeah, um, tell him
I'll be up in a sec.

36:35.944 --> 36:39.615
