you never loved me...

36:39.698 --> 36:42.492
Hey, Belly. How you holding up?

36:42.576 --> 36:43.827
Okay.

36:43.911 --> 36:46.788
Um, have you seen
Conrad anywhere?

36:46.872 --> 36:49.666
Yeah. Yeah, I think
I saw him go to the rec room.

36:49.750 --> 36:53.003
Oh, yeah? Yeah?
Um, okay. Thank you.

36:53.086 --> 36:54.296
- Okay.
- Yeah.

36:54.379 --> 36:58.133
♪ Baby, I don't wanna know ♪

37:01.345 --> 37:04.932
- ♪ Oh, no ♪
- [clears throat]

37:05.015 --> 37:09.603
