40:46.153 --> 40:47.696
♪ Who am I to blame? ♪

40:47.779 --> 40:50.323
♪ Who am I to blame, though? ♪

40:52.576 --> 40:54.369
♪ And I cannot be changed ♪

40:54.452 --> 40:57.122
♪ I cannot be changed, no ♪

40:57.205 --> 40:59.583
♪ Trust me, I've tried ♪

41:00.792 --> 41:04.671
♪ I just end up right at
the start of the line...

41:04.754 --> 41:06.548
I'm sorry about this morning.

41:06.631 --> 41:10.886
I think I was... scared that

41:10.969 --> 41:13.722
you guys were gonna
see me fuck everything up.

41:16.641 --> 41:18.894
♪ Well, I drink my whiskey...

41:18.977 --> 41:21.813
I'm glad you were there
to talk to Dad with me, though.

41:22.814 --> 41:24.316
♪ We're doin' well...

41:24.399 --> 41:25.859
Aunt Julia was a stretch,

41:25.942 --> 41:28.945
but I really thought
I could convince Dad.

41:29.029 --> 41:30.739
[chuckles]

41:30.822 --> 41:33.366
You kept me from completely
tearing into him, so...

41:33.450 --> 41:35.535
It's no easy feat.

41:37.370 --> 41:40.582
♪ Do not be afraid,
do not be afraid...

41:40.665 --> 41:42.792
You know, I just feel
everyone's slipping away,

41:42.876 --> 41:45.295
